ifncli
=====

ifncli is a set of python library to work with Influenzanet platform and a set of command line tools.

The package is organized in several modules :

- api : embeds all function & info about the Influenzanet API
- surveys : library to work with surveys
  - influenzanet : Influenzanet survey models & tools
  - standard : Influenzanet standard survey definition (to commmon survey questions)
  - tools : tools to read, print, validate & check surveys
- managers : set of modules embedding complex actions (to be used in command line but could be reused for web ui for example)
  - messaging : messages tools
- platform: platform configuration, handle the informations about the targeted platform (like kubectl context, how to connect, credentials, and common configurations)
